  "text": "The notation specific to problem (C k ) (resp., (R β )) is based on the letter \"c\" (resp., the letter \"r\"). Lowercase (resp., uppercase) letters stand for optimal values (resp., optimal sets). Furthermore: − L := min k ∈ I N c k = 0 where c k is the optimal value of problem (C k ) defined in [CITATION_1] .",
